{"tid":1042560,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日飲涼茶個陣，隔離個中學生","createTime":"2019-03-01T15:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T02:09:33.000Z","uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0efbfb4b0e336e780324f3680a26ad411b961bec","tid":1042560,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"阿姨，上火飲乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n我當堂。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上火？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老味，熱氣啊！<br />\n上你老母火</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c66d1a89ed630664936a741f57b1422ae8add58","tid":1042560,"uid":224107,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"熱氣，是中醫術語，民間俗語<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">上火</span></strong>。中醫認為人體陰陽失衡，內火旺盛，即會上火(熱氣)。所謂的「火」是形容身體內某些熱性的症狀。而熱氣也就是人體陰陽失衡後出現的內熱症。症狀包括眼睛紅腫、口角糜爛、尿黃和牙齒痛等。"},{"pid":"2e703abcd2ccbe860029520c1b82046169cc6259","tid":1042560,"uid":114097,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"阿姨 緊火飲咩啊"},{"pid":"92ab2080486944f8af0735e45efcf76a066e10b8","tid":1042560,"uid":231317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e703abcd2ccbe860029520c1b82046169cc6259","tid":1042560,"uid":114097,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"阿姨 緊火飲咩啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"吞精好呀"},{"pid":"a035b65198575119de330bf05bfcc937f772353e","tid":1042560,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92ab2080486944